Uses of Interface
builtins.Command

Packages that use Command
Package
Description
builtins
Contains all built-in shell command implementations (cd, pwd, echo, exit, type, history, etc.).
core
Contains the core logic for the shell, including the main entry point, command handler, history, input handling, tab completion, and tokenization.
